Message.SourceString: I've got something to give you, but you've got your hands full. Go clear some space and then come back to me.
Message.LocalizedString: I've got something to give you, but you've got your hands full. Go clear some space and then come back to me.

Message.SourceString: He disappeared after we got the lodestone working, vanished before you arrived. I'd like to track him down. To do that I need to cast a locator spell.
Message.LocalizedString: He disappeared after we got the lodestone working, vanished before you arrived. I'd like to track him down. To do that I need to cast a locator spell.

Message.SourceString: Not finished yet? The longer you leave things, the more likely you are to become a dragon's dinner.
Message.LocalizedString: Not finished yet? The longer you leave things, the more likely you are to become a dragon's dinner.

Message.SourceString: You can go bigger, of course, let your inner architect run wild, but the bed's the bare minimum we need to get started. Go on, hop to it. Get!
Message.LocalizedString: You can go bigger, of course, let your inner architect run wild, but the bed's the bare minimum we need to get started. Go on, hop to it. Get!

Message.SourceString: We should build our new base of operations here. By we, I mean you -- bad back.
Message.LocalizedString: We should build our new base of operations here. By we, I mean you -- bad back.

Message.SourceString: Good, you've got the basics under your belt, but now the guide ropes are off. Taking down a dragon won't be easy, but you've got the skills you need to do it. Well... almost.
Message.LocalizedString: Good, you've got the basics under your belt, but now the guide ropes are off. Taking down a dragon won't be easy, but you've got the skills you need to do it. Well... almost.

Message.SourceString: Doesn't need to be fancy -- though style is always worth pursuing -- but it needs to be functional. Make a shelter, some foundations, walls, and a roof, and then build and claim a bed in it.
Message.LocalizedString: Doesn't need to be fancy -- though style is always worth pursuing -- but it needs to be functional. Make a shelter, some foundations, walls, and a roof, and then build and claim a bed in it.

Message.SourceString: We need to start thinking long term. Bramblemead village is an excellent place for an outpost, even if it's a little overrun with goblins right now.
Message.LocalizedString: We need to start thinking long term. Bramblemead village is an excellent place for an outpost, even if it's a little overrun with goblins right now.

Message.SourceString: We should build our new base of operations here. By we, I mean you -- bad back.
Message.LocalizedString: We should build our new base of operations here. By we, I mean you -- bad back.

Message.SourceString: Doesn't need to be fancy -- though style is always worth pursuing -- but it needs to be functional. Make a shelter, some foundations, walls, and a roof, and then build and claim a bed in it.
Message.LocalizedString: Doesn't need to be fancy -- though style is always worth pursuing -- but it needs to be functional. Make a shelter, some foundations, walls, and a roof, and then build and claim a bed in it.

Message.SourceString: I'm just missing one ingredient, which I'll need from you. Antlers. You can get them from deer, hunt one and bring me the antlers. Then we'll get started. But first, here, take this.
Message.LocalizedString: I'm just missing one ingredient, which I'll need from you. Antlers. You can get them from deer, hunt one and bring me the antlers. Then we'll get started. But first, here, take this.

Message.SourceString: Anyway, look, we're set up here, but there's one of our number missing. Young Cathan, an adventurer in training that came along with us.
Message.LocalizedString: Anyway, look, we're set up here, but there's one of our number missing. Young Cathan, an adventurer in training that came along with us.

Message.SourceString: I've got something to give you, but you've got your hands full. Go clear some space and then come back to me.
Message.LocalizedString: I've got something to give you, but you've got your hands full. Go clear some space and then come back to me.

Message.SourceString: Good, you've built a shelter. I mean... it could do with some work, we're gonna be here a while. Have you considered the decor at all?
Message.LocalizedString: Good, you've built a shelter. I mean... it could do with some work, we're gonna be here a while. Have you considered the decor at all?

Message.SourceString: You can go bigger, of course, let your inner architect run wild, but the bed's the bare minimum we need to get started. Go on, hop to it. Get!
Message.LocalizedString: You can go bigger, of course, let your inner architect run wild, but the bed's the bare minimum we need to get started. Go on, hop to it. Get!

Message.SourceString: Maybe some better lighting? Curtains? A single potted plant? *Sigh* no, no, you're right. It's not important. Why live it up when there's so much squalor to enjoy?
Message.LocalizedString: Maybe some better lighting? Curtains? A single potted plant? *Sigh* no, no, you're right. It's not important. Why live it up when there's so much squalor to enjoy?

Properties.TextName: Return to the Wise old man after claimed bed
